<div class="wrapper">
  <%= render :partial => "slider", :locals => {:btitle => @btitle, :stitle => @stitle, :search_text => @search_text} %>

  <div id="theword" class="container content-sm">
      <div class="text-center margin-bottom-50">
          <h2 class="title-v2 title-center">再見手札的特色</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="row content-boxes-v4">
          <div class="col-md-4 md-margin-bottom-40">
              <i class="pull-left fa fa-lightbulb-o"></i>
              <div class="content-boxes-in-v4">
                  <h2>完整溝通</h2>
                  <p>器捐意願、安寧意願、醫療訣擇、喪葬意願，再見手札讓您完整且方便的與家人溝通意願</p>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 md-margin-bottom-40">
              <i class="pull-left fa fa-flash"></i>
              <div class="content-boxes-in-v4">
                  <h2>快速分享</h2>
                  <p>再見手札可以快速分享您的意願給家人，輕鬆溝通這些嚴肅的議題，也希望您能分享給親朋好友，邀請大家一起加入器官捐贈的行列!</p>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
              <i class="pull-left fa fa-compress"></i>
              <div class="content-boxes-in-v4">
                  <h2>方便查詢</h2>
                  <p>不同於健保卡註記，再見手札讓家人隨⼿就能查詢您的意願</p>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
  </div>

  <div id="theword" class="row fill-all-form">
    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 col-xs-12 byenote-title">
      <h2 class="">再見手札</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 col-xs-12 form-page tag-box-v2 byenote-form-page">

      <%= form_for(@byenote) do |f| %>
        <%= render :partial => "organ_form", :locals => {:f => f} %>
        <%= render :partial => "hospice_form", :locals => {:f => f} %>
        <%= render :partial => "funeral_form", :locals => {:f => f} %>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="heading"><h3 style="text-align:center;"><legend>給親友的話</legend></h3></div>
          <%= f.text_area :some_message, rows: 4, :class => "message_textarea", :placeholder => "告訴親友你寫下器官捐贈、安寧及喪葬意願的原因 (注意: 此項目開放不特定人查詢及閱覽，請避免個人隱私資訊)" %>
        <div class="margin-bottom-20"></div>
          <p>*為便於查詢，以上資料開放任何人查詢及閱覽，請避免個人隱私資訊</p>
          <%= f.submit "儲存我的再見手札",:style => "width:100%;padding:10px;", :class => "btn btn-u" %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%= render :partial => "contactus", :locals => { } %>
</div>


